    <div class="row mobile-center">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <h4>Years of Chopper Experience</h4>
        <p>We eat, breath, and sleep motorcycles. Carter Customs' founder, Chad Carter, can't remember a time when bikes were not his passion. Now, he has transformed his shop into the ultimate work space. Whatever dreams you've got for your ride, Carter Customs will work to make it a reality.</p>
        <%= image_tag "line_art/lines.png", class: "line-image-wide" %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <%= image_tag "line_art/motorcycle_sketch.png", style: "width: 100%; opacity: 0.1" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

